- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper discusses a data processing technique for improving time delay estimation, which falls under the domain of control systems. 
- cs.SI (Signal and Image Processing): The paper deals with signal processing techniques such as the power cepstrum and autocorrelation. 
- cs.NA (Numerical Analysis): The paper involves numerical techniques for analyzing the output spectrogram and generating the power cepstrum. 
- cs.IT (Information Theory): The paper involves the use of information theory concepts such as the power cepstrum to extract useful information from the input signal.
